  m_Text: 'Run a single manually configured benchmark.



    Run the full automated
    benchmark matrix.



    Covers all combinations of:

    - 3 timer drivers (Rx,
    Coroutine, Update)

    - 4 timer types (Delay, Interval, Timer, Countdown)

    -
    5 concurrency levels (1, 10, 100, 500, 1000 instances)



    60 scenarios x
    5 repeats. GC is collected before every run for clean measurements. Results are
    aggregated (mean, std dev, min, max, median, p95) and saved to a single CSV.



    Estimated
    runtime: ~25 min'
